data.description: Nestled in the desirable Arbor Greens community of Arvada, this delightful 2-story townhome offers both comfort and convenience. Featuring 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this residence is perfect for first-time buyers or those seeking a low-maintenance lifestyle. The home boasts a functional galley-style kitchen, freshly painted interiors, and a $5,000 concession to make it truly yours—choose to invest in new carpeting, apply it towards closing costs for reduced upfront expenses, buy down your rate for lower monthly payments, or simply reduce the purchase price. The possibilities are tailored to your needs! Step outside to a private, FULLY FENCED-PRIVATE FRONT YARD - ideal for relaxation or a playful day with your pet. Residents of Arbor Greens enjoy access to exclusive amenities including two clubhouses and a refreshing seasonal pool, perfect for enjoying those warm summer days. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own in one of Arvada's most sought-after neighborhoods. For more details or to arrange your private showing, please contact listing agent, Stacia Shane, at 720-434-7375. Act quickly, as this gem won’t be available for long! Showings start Friday, May 3rd.
